        "content": "<p>Just as we have <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/set.image2\">docs#set.image2</a>, should we have <code>filter.comap₂</code>? I'm staring at <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/filter.has_mul\">docs#filter.has_mul</a> to see whether we can abstract something away.</p>",
